Name: USCoreCDARoleCode
Title: USCore CCDA Role Code
Descriptino: **FHIR Version R4 Copy of FHIR Version R5 [CDARoleCode](http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/ValueSet/CDARoleCode).** A set of codes further specifying the kind of Role; specific classification codes for further qualifying RoleClass codes.

Descriptino: The US Core Clinical Note Type Value Set is a 'starter set' of types supported for fetching and storing clinical notes.
